# Line endings.
#
# Pinakes is authored from Windows, from Linux (Fly.io), and from cloud agent
# sessions. Without a normalization rule the same file committed from two of
# those places can differ on every line and read as a full-file rewrite.
#
# `text=auto` lets Git decide which files are text; `eol=lf` pins both the
# committed blob and the working-copy checkout to LF on every platform.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — exempt from line-ending and textual conversion.
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.png  binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.pdf  binary
*.docx binary
